This is the form you need to complete to add a secondary user to update your modpack. This form should be completed by the new user that needs permission to update a modpack with the aid of the original creator.

Pack Name:
Required

The pack name as it appears in the original post


Link:
Required

Link to the original thread. Note: you will not have permission to view this link, you should obtain it from the original pack creator


The original pack creator now needs to create a post allowing you to update their modpack, the post should contain the following content:

"I give {username} permission to update my modpack"
